I did notice as I've gotten older lack of hobbies because more and more obvious because in the off time you're not busy it's like what do you really do ya know? You sometimes just sit there and wonder "Man, does that really make me happy?" Sorry, I'm rambling but if it's of any help, Hololive EN especially you Gura have really helped me deal with a lot of personal stuff in my life. Ending of a relationship, best friends of 7-8 years and I basically going to not being able to stand one another, family members getting sick and further on. I really appreciate ALL of you and have wanted to do a superchat to you thanking you for all that but maybe that'd be an essay and idk if anyone would read it lol. Not only have you helped me through  worst times in my 27 years of living but I've been able to sleep, I sometimes put past streams on because it helps me feel not as bad.

Thank you Gura
